    "skill": "Words in Context",
    "difficulty": "Hard",
    "passage": "While scholars believe many Mesoamerican cities influenced each other, direct evidence of such influence is difficult to ascertain.\nHowever, recent excavations in a sector of Tikal (Guatemala) unearthed a citadel that shows ______ Teotihuac\u00e1n (Mexico)\narchitecture\u2014including a near replica of a famed Teotihuac\u00e1n temple\u2014providing tangible evidence of outside influence in portions\nof Tikal.",
    "question": "Which choice completes the text with the most logical and precise word or phrase?",
