    "skill": "Words in Context",
    "difficulty": "Hard",
    "passage": "The following text is adapted from George Eliot\u2019s 1871\u201372 novel Middlemarch.\n[Mr. Brooke] had travelled in his younger years, and was held in this part of the country to have contracted a too rambling\nhabit of mind. Mr. Brooke\u2019s conclusions were as difficult to predict as the weather.",
