    "skill": "Words in Context",
    "difficulty": "Hard",
    "passage": "During a 2014 archaeological dig in Spain, Vicente Lull and his team uncovered the skeleton of a woman from El Algar, an Early\nBronze Age society, buried with valuable objects signaling a high position of power. This finding may persuade researchers who\nhave argued that Bronze Age societies were ruled by men to ______ that women may have also held leadership roles.",
    "question": "Which choice completes the text with the most logical and precise word or phrase?",
