    "skill": "Words in Context",
    "difficulty": "Medium",
    "passage": "Domesticated thousands of years ago by Indigenous people in South America, cacao, the plant from which chocolate is made,\ndeviates structurally from the wild plant it is descended from. Maize (corn), another crop domesticated by Indigenous Americans,\nshows so little resemblance to any wild plant that genetic research was necessary to ______ teosinte grass as its ancestor.",
